  "remarks": "JSC Mashinostroyeniya is responsible for producing and designing the P-800 Oniks (Onyx) missile, which is used by the Russian Armed Forces in the war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, JSC Mashinostroyeniya is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. Furthermore, JSC Mashinostroyeniya is also associated with JSC Tactical Missiles Corporation.",
